properties.text: Heaven's Point stands tall above Castle Moss...
The Moss-Knights Stand Alone against the Armies of Heaven
Keep an eye out for CASTLE SIGILS, they may unravel the mysteries of Castle Moss.
No one knows what lies within the bowels of the Penitent Tower, as only the Angelic wards of this world are allowed within.
BEWARE: Undead. Be sure to HOLD your weapon in front of you!
